*Poljubac* joj je bio topao i pun ljubavi. (Her kiss was warm and full of love.)

Njih dvoje su se dugo čuvali u *poljubcu*. (The two of them lingered in the kiss for a long time.)

Ona je dala ljubavnom *poljubcu* njegove usne. (She kissed his lips with love.)

*Poljubci* su lepilo njihovih srca. (Kisses were glue for their hearts.)

Ona je sve vreme držala njegov *poljubac*. (She kept his kiss all the time.)